{"tid":2229931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯去信顧委會投訴遭鏗鏘集針對 廣播處長梁家榮：追查真相節目難免令人感冒犯","createTime":"2020-10-04T16:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T17:05:15.000Z","uid":365024,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"83d4378bf3c49bf2de48114a7e4e28f94a2f5c50","tid":2229931,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:33:33.000Z","msg":"【何君堯去信顧委會 　稱遭《鏗鏘集》針對】<br />\n【梁家榮：追查真相節目難免令人感冒犯】<br />\n<br />\n港台顧問委員會最新、7月31日的公開會議紀錄顯示，立法會議員何君堯去信顧委會，投訴 《鏗鏘集：721 誰主真相》記者在訪問中針對他。<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>廣播處長梁家榮在會上表示，兩集關於「721 事件」的《鏗鏘集》，無論從新聞學、紀錄片、追查等角度，製作水準足以作為新聞學的教材和典範，認為此類追查真相節目，有時難免會令某些人感到冒犯，因而引來激烈反應。</strong></span></span>梁家榮表示，信件反映社會對「721 事件」仍看法紛陳，港台不會放棄任何一個角度跟進。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #港台電視31 #港台電視32 #十點半新聞天地 #721元朗事件<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYAtEkn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYAtEkn.jpg&h=9842ab27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3902501423191218/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F3902501423191218%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil5nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=51a11235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3902501423191218/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"fc5c01031bbdf327695765c8551639aa94b5be38","tid":2229931,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb95541c5da8f6937ba0e73becd2677f225547ec","tid":2229931,"uid":260251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/